, Regression) -- can be\ncarried over to the realm of deep learning as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 20 Jun 2020 20:26:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2020 02:02:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-10"}
